title: For the Friday Night LOLS
description:
In the midst of all the high tensions in these troubled times, I figured I would gift you all with a few moments of hilarity...my reaction to a random huffpost quiz guessing what my generation I was born in based on my vernacular. 

If you are interested here is the quiz: https://play.howstuffworks.com/quiz/tell-us-how-you-speak-well-guess-youre-gen-x-baby-boomer-millennial?fbclid=IwAR2_97qlHgUXhXqwL8ytYLkoO9Y6F0yqlKS_PvWQqA-esE5q_Lpjs8cK8p4

Follow me on twitter here: @AndreaLynnLewis
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
